20524d74ec","tid":2377040,"uid":342282,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T17:29:43.000Z","msg":"史達林格勒戰役<br />\n士兵平均存活時間不超過24小時"},{"pid":"ca6db9cc684eb3cab6d0cc34c3ab7f678da47616","tid":2377040,"uid":262677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T18:08:52.000Z","msg":"二戰嗰陣美國有派考察團去中共控制嘅區域度視察，而成員事後多數對中共持有正面評價，後嚟亦因為麥卡錫主義被打壓<br />\n<br />\n喺日本投降之後，美國派陸戰隊暫時管理冇俾蘇聯佔領嘅地方，等之後再交翻俾國民黨。呢啲陸戰隊執行任務期間受到中共遊擊隊嘅伏擊同騷擾，亦係二戰唯一同中共軍打過嘅美軍部隊"},{"pid":"16f367655ce312f031275ea10516cee594db42b9","tid":2377040,"uid":373438,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T18:16:53.000Z","msg":"何東家族同其他香港有錢佬曾經投資落去陳炯明推動廣東獨立 目的係反對國民黨北伐(因為省港大罷工係國民黨推動令商會當國民黨係左派威脅)<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：香。港。民。族。論"},{"pid":"54fd9a79cd38e7856ef3882446bbade538266851","tid":2377040,"uid":56302,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"306850c488c8bd1b1b42dc4f63701d41f51157ef","tid":2377040,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"明帝國殖民越南廿年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T22:24:21.000Z","msg":"明成祖個時係建立布政司納為國土<br />\n點都稱唔上係殖民"},{"pid":"8562c020d61d347bc22161be1c5491d5dae4fe13","tid":2377040,"uid":33749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T23:40:34.000Z","msg":"嶺南好多所謂嘅南遷正統中原人<br />\n其實係漢化咗嘅原居民<br />\n佢哋老作自己嘅族史<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/122577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F122577&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TagDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=de85e06c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/122577</a>"},{"pid":"1fc27c3b16bd12506d5864ce6a36e491db2bd0a7","tid":2377040,"uid":218716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c504514c1439100a99dcaf67c8f42f308988de6","tid":2377040,"uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"Mark Zuckerberg 老豆老母都